OL,6,FIn a summary of the Court of Appeal's
OL,7,Fdecision not to change the sentence of
OL,8,Ftriple killer Valdo Calocane, the Lady
OL,9,FChief Justice Baroness Carr said: "It
OL,10,Fis impossible to read of the
OL,11,Fcircumstances of this offending
OL,12,Fwithout the greatest possible sympathy
OL,13,Ffor the victims of these terrible
OL,14,Fattacks, and their family and friends.
OL,16,F"The victim impact statements paint a
OL,17,Fgraphic picture of the appalling
OL,18,Feffects of the offender's conduct.
OL,26,@qD@cOUxD@AOU
