OL,6,F"Had the offender not suffered the
OL,7,Fmental condition that he did, the
OL,8,Fsentencing judge would doubtless have
OL,9,Fbeen considering a whole life term.
OL,11,F"But neither the judge nor this court
OL,12,Fcan ignore the medical evidence as to
OL,13,Fthe offender's condition which led to
OL,14,Fthese dreadful events or the threat to
OL,15,Fpublic safety which the offender
OL,16,Fcontinues to pose."
