OL,6,FThe mother of Barnaby Webber, who was
OL,7,F19, says the outcome of the Court of
OL,8,FAppeal hearing "proves how utterly
OL,9,Fflawed and under-resourced the
OL,10,Fcriminal justice system in the UK is".
OL,12,FIn a statement following the Court of
OL,13,FAppeal's decision, Emma Webber said:
OL,14,F"Today's ruling comes as no surprise
OL,15,Fto the families of the Nottingham
OL,16,Fattack victims. It was inevitable and
OL,17,Fwas not a review of anything other
OL,18,Fthan the letter of the law as it
OL,19,Fstands.
