OL,6,F"Despite the fact that the Attorney
OL,7,FGeneral herself feels that Valdo
OL,8,FCalocane did not receive the
OL,9,Fappropriate sentence, today's outcome
OL,10,Fproves how utterly flawed and under-
OL,11,Fresourced the criminal justice system
OL,12,Fin the UK is. It also illustrates the
OL,13,Fneed for urgent reforms in the UK
OL,14,Fhomicide law.
