OL,4,CNottingham attacks killer's sentence
OL,6,F"The fact remains, despite the words
OL,7,Fof the judge, that almost 90% of
OL,8,Fpeople serving hospital orders are out
OL,9,Fwithin 10 years and 98% within 20
OL,10,Fyears. In effect, the families now
OL,11,Fface their own life sentence of
OL,12,Fensuring the monster that is Valdo
OL,13,FCalocane becomes the next Ian Brady or
OL,14,FFred West and is never released.
OL,16,F"Given the failed investigation
OL,17,Fcarried out by Nottingham Police, the
OL,18,Fweak prosecution put forward by East
OL,19,FMidlands CPS and the over-reliance on
OL,20,Fdoctors' reports, there was probably
OL,21,Fno other conclusion that could be made.
OL,26,@nD@AOUxD@AOU
