OL,6,F"The families have raised their
OL,7,Fconcerns already with the Government
OL,8,Fwith regard to obvious errors and
OL,9,Fomissions that have resulted in this
OL,10,Ftragedy."
OL,12,FSpeaking outside the Royal Courts of
OL,13,FJustice following the Court of
OL,14,FAppeal's refusal to change the
OL,15,Fsentence of Valdo Calocane, Dr Sanjoy
OL,16,FKumar, father of victim Grace O'Malley-
OL,17,FKumar, said: "The Attorney General's
OL,18,Fcase has not been successful. This is
OL,19,Fdisappointing, but not unexpected.
