OL,3,CCourt of Appeal refuses to change
OL,4,CNottingham attacks killer's sentence
OL,6,F"The Nottingham attacks were entirely
OL,7,Fpreventable. Nottinghamshire Police
OL,8,Ffailed to produce a warrant for many
OL,9,Fmonths, a flawed investigation, no
OL,10,Ftoxicology, over-reliance on
OL,11,Fpsychiatric reports.
OL,13,F"Leicestershire Police failed to
OL,14,Farrest Valdo Calocane. This is a
OL,15,Ffailure of two police forces, a
OL,16,Ffailure of the mental health trust,
OL,17,Falong with Nottinghamshire (County)
OL,18,FCouncil as well.
