OL,6,F"Missed multiple opportunities to
OL,7,Fprevent the Nottingham attacks and the
OL,8,Fmurder of our children and Ian Coates
OL,9,Fis what has led us here today. We have
OL,10,Fcontinued to pursue agencies that
OL,11,Ffailed us and hold them responsible
OL,12,Ffor the Nottingham attacks, so that no
OL,13,Fother family is made to suffer like
OL,14,Fours.
OL,16,F"We thank everyone for the outpouring
OL,17,Fof support for our brave and beautiful
OL,18,Fdaughter, Grace."
